Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Municipality of Ponot in Zamboanga Del Norte to Jose Dalman
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 381
An Act Changing the Name of the Municipality of Ponot in Zamboanga Del Norte to Jose Dalman
Section 1. The name of the Municipality of Ponot in the Province of Zamboanga del Norte is hereby changed to Jose Dalman.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 8, 1983
